#week-title("Three", "Melissa officinalis — The Gateway Herb")

=== Core Teaching

Lemon Balm (*Melissa officinalis*) is the chosen gateway herb for the Tyro. It is
gentle, widely available, and responds clearly to basic spagyric treatment. It is
ruled by *Jupiter* (secondarily solar) and is associated with spiritual
elevation, clarity of mind, and the restoration of the vital spirit.

Timing the Work to the cosmic pattern is essential. Begin operations during the
*planetary hour of Jupiter* (on Thursday) for maximum alignment with the plant's
virtue. This is not superstition — it is the timing of the Work to the tides of
the World Spirit.

