=== Topics This Week

- Melissa officinalis: planetary rulership, signature, and history
- Sourcing high-quality dried herbs
- Calculating planetary hours and days
- Alternative herbs: Lavender, Caraway, and Rosemary

#inner-work[
  *The Inner Flame in the Laboratory*

  Before entering the laboratory for each session, spend three minutes with the
  *Inner Flame* practice. Let the inner fire and the outer fire of the laboratory
  begin to feel like one thing. Notice how your internal state of attention
  impacts your manual dexterity and observation in the lab.
]

